Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:15.30,Staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片源\Nchiwa\N\N\N　壓製\N　xelnaga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#04 國一課程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午餐吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達﹐拜託妳買的書呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有﹐不准妳再買了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的菜單每次都是\N咖哩、漢堡肉和炒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦﹐挑食的話會長不大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放馬鈴薯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行﹐會長不大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經長得夠大了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始﹐妳要去國中上學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦﹐妳有話想說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非得去上學不可？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說﹐像妳這種小鬼\N白天在外面晃來晃去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰居的太太們會誤會的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為有什麼不可告人的內幕\N或者遭到虐待什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要理他們就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一被通報到\N警察局或區公所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭痛的可是你們喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被警察抓去輔導
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是被人蛇綁架\N賣到香港或澳門之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的去上學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被綁架？妳以為我幾歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常都會反遭艾妮達修理就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:04:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是被賣到香港\N可以省下回家的交通費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成我意見的人舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多數暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭\N不要干涉人家的隱私好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且文件和手續之類的\N要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我已經先偽造好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護照我也準備好了\N妳要帶在身上喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學費怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是超級窮光蛋耶\N被這些書害的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心﹐我有門路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊﹐難道是讀仙社？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那裡薪水最好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡那裡的工作\N總覺得是在騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道李先生會不會給我們年假？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是香港來的留學生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達．金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要用力跟她做好朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？\N沒有精神喔﹐金同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話\N能不能直接叫我名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題﹐艾妮達\N這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回答“是”﹐once again
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菱石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的隔壁是艾妮達的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相處喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達﹐打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也要給她打氣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮冬瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是不是把這裡\N跟小學搞錯了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小徹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧\N因為這裡有你這種小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吵架喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好﹐我叫菱石久美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難唸喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以叫妳小久嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達在學校\N不曉得還順利嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在異國的土地\N被陌生人團團圍住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過﹐艾妮達應該應付得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為監護人﹐我還是偷偷地\N到學校保護她比較好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬﹐麻煩妳保護老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有﹐等一下讀仙社\N如果打電話來﹐幫我接一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傍晚就會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳只是想出去玩而已吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,l ganna make him an offer\Nhe can't refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句找…岡原﹐翻譯看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？come on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…對他…他的不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難了嗎？\N好﹐後面的艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是﹐我想提出一個\N他無法拒絕的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了﹐表現不錯喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,congflation﹐艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是congratulations（恭喜）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀﹐老師也要加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔﹐金同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我艾妮達就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的日文是跟誰學的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姊姊他們在當口譯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有姊姊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個很高跟一個很輕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會讀跟寫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點而已﹐現在正在學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們寄宿在一位作家的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位作家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫堇川奈奈奈\N你們知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有聽過這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小久﹐妳是不是有看過\N這個作家的書？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達．金同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到日本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:09:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫西園夏梅\N請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了歡迎遠渡重洋\N來到日本的艾妮達．金同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在暢銷排行榜竄升中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送妳超大型新人\N西園春日的衝擊處女作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“開始初戀”的親筆簽名書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西園？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀﹐妳注意到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯﹐不瞞妳說﹐她就是我姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為親妹妹的我\N也讀到感動落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一本超棒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她全班同學都送了一本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來﹐不用客氣﹐收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思﹐我心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達可能比較喜歡\N堇川老師的小說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說我姊姊的書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸給那種化石小說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:10:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的﹐我討厭看書\N只是因為這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生好像在吵架耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有毛病\N跟妳實在聊不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的﹐對不起\N因為校門關起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就該走後門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說的也是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生不能只走正門\N有時候走後門也是一種學習
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖滾樂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖滾樂？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇﹐艾妮達好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在香港有參加過球隊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊\N艾妮達．金同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才是我的勁敵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過﹐妳的精彩表現\N也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用我的殺人殺球\N讓妳瞧瞧日本的實力…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幾時變成她的勁敵了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要發球了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡原﹐球來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生﹐危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達﹐妳喜歡喝牛奶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯﹐對身體很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的給妳喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這麼多我喝不下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個轉學生還真敢開口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡大概沒東西吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在家裡也吃得好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小徹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫得那麼親暱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說岡原啊\N你幹嘛對艾妮達那麼凶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啦﹐是這傢伙先來惹我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似衝突的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是表示被對方強烈吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是羅曼史的王道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會喜歡這種迷你猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這句話是我要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然滿臉通紅的否定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個害羞的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才討厭女生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論什麼事都要扯到那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是我家沒東西吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西園也有點怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過﹐艾妮達\N妳還不習慣這種玩笑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,習慣的人才有毛病\N我們才國一耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經國一了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個學姊要找妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跑來幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很擔心妳\N在家裡坐立難安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼要穿成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說穿這樣\N比較容易混進來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？好不好看？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳饒了我吧﹐我什麼都沒做\N就已經夠引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊﹐我放心多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好像已經交了很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…該怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有討厭的傢伙\N也有奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才好啊\N學校本來就是這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要創造許多美好的回憶喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達﹐妳有空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了﹐艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級的學姊\N她來問我香港的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們學校有這種美人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了﹐老師\N你找我有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於社團活動的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起﹐我馬上準備午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我要出去一個禮拜）\N（你們就自己看著辦吧　奈奈奈）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動啊\N真的非參加不可嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是校規
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那麼厲害\N大家一定都會很歡迎妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運動神經又很發達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不想\N到學校還要運動耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好驚人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在一年級裡面\N已經是超級人氣王了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像動物園的貓熊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小久﹐妳參加什麼社團？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了﹐我要參加妳的社團\N帶我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好﹐走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走﹐快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好﹐我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊﹐我又輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大貧民﹐請快點發牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好﹐這次一定要變大富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我可是不會輸的喔\N-是是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起喔\N妳明明說過很討厭書…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦\N是我叫妳帶我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且因為我姊姊他們的關係\N讓我已經得到免疫力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一點書﹐還勉強可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理查先生﹐你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨﹐妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是今天加入圖書社的新同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是理查先生\N在販賣英語教材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看一下書喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小久﹐圖書社要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是看書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:17:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有管理圖書館\N寫讀後心得參加比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過﹐好像沒什麼人來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有人氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過﹐感覺像是自己\N獨佔了這些書﹐很開心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有堇川老師的書喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理查先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去叫醫生來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書…幫我藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久美…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼…是個小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險﹐大家快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用紙？\N那些女孩用紙攻擊妳是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裘克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用這個名字叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了﹐沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過﹐任務一定要徹底執行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出那本書﹐並將它弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於那些女孩的情報\N也要逐一向我報告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過﹐如果也像我們\N在做這種工作的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有點可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐？我差點就被他殺了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜姊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是什麼樣的敵人\N什麼樣的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有辦法殺死妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心﹐我們一定會保護妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和瑪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們回來了\N-我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊﹐老師她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊﹐她又出門了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師經常這樣突然就失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在老師回來之前\N你們就放假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是﹐那我們就請年假囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一般請假而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就讓我們請個年假嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一般請假而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.48,0:21:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊﹐這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦﹐是那個人帶來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡﹐你太囂張了喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去﹐馬上給我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了沒\N討厭﹐下去啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬﹐艾妮達\N有工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:25.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍藏的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:31.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是凋零散落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:35.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有和你的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:40.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深烙在我心深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:47.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸轉涼的海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:53.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人嬉戲的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:57.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你曬得黝黑的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:03.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融化在西沉的夕陽裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:08.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願牽著的手永不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:16.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣長大成人該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:23.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陽光下追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:27.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:34.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到戀情結束的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:38.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互依偎
